headline: U.S. tourist Jessica Colker killed in Grenada
content: By Doug Criss and Shawn Nottingham, CNNUpdated 2045 GMT (0445 HKT) January 26, 2016  (CNN)American tourist Jessica Colker died from an "extensive skull fracture and asphyxia," according to autopsy results the Royal Grenada Police Force released Tuesday. CNN's Tristan Smith and Eliott C. McLaughlin contributed to this report.
